<ul><li><a href="/wiki/Dead_bell" title="Dead bell">Dead bell</a>, used to announce deaths and funerals.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Street_cries" title="Street cries">Street cries</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Message_stick" title="Message stick">Message stick</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Umalohokan" title="Umalohokan">Umalohokan</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Vic_Garth" title="Vic Garth">Vic Garth</a>, reputed in 2005 to be the oldest town crier in the world.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Knocker-up" title="Knocker-up">Knocker-up</a>, the antiquated profession of human alarm clock.</li></ul>
